net.tridentsdk.server.entity

Class EntityBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.tridentsdk.server.entity.EntityBuilder

  • public final class EntityBuilder
extends Object
    Builds an entity from initializer components and auto-spawns safely

    This is not thread safe. Do not share across methods, and you should be good.

    Author:
    The TridentSDK Team
